  2008) for <span style="font-style: italic">Notre Dame Philosophical Reviews</span> (2008).</li>
																	  <li><a href="http://www.arsdisputandi.org/publish/articles/000265/article.pdf" target="_blank">Review of Paul Boghossian's  <em>Fear  of Knowledge</em></a> (Oxford: Clarendon, 2006) for <em>Ars Disputandi</em>, Vol. 7 (2007).</li>
																      <li><a href="http://www.arsdisputandi.org/publish/articles/000227/article.pdf" target="_blank">Review of Maria Baghramian's <span style="font-style: italic">Relativism</span></a> (London: Routledge, 2004) for <span style="font-style: italic">Ars Disputandi</span>, Vol. 6 (2006).</li>
															      </ul>
